1.9.0 2013-09-26T12:07:46Z
 [00 Major]
 - Well not hugely major, declared develop depends change starting this release.
 - @Author::KENTNL is develop_required ( as you will need that bundle if you do any dev work on consuming things
   without modifiying them )
 - @Author::KENTNL::Lite is now develop_suggests only, to indicate that bundle can be somewhat used to work on
   consuming things, as long as you edit the right dist.ini's to make it so.

