 - Upgrade deps to avoid rt#67183

 [Dependencies::Stats]
 - Dependencies changed since 1.0.3, see Changes.deps* for details
 - runtime: ↑1

 [Features]
 - Removed extra whitespace padding on injected release stamp lines. This results in the generated file being the same
   as a parsed and re-serialized version of the same file as per how CPAN::Changes sees it.

 [Packaging]
 - Rebuilt with rt#67183 test annoyance solved.

