0.01023311 2011-01-01T19:31:37Z
 [BugFixes]
 - Ini generation previously produced "Prereq" instead of the now-standard "Prereqs". This is now fixed.

 [Dependencies::Stats]
 - Dependencies changed since 0.01017322, see Changes.deps* for details
 - runtime: +2

 [Features]
 - Ships now with minting profile 'Author::KENTNL'. New dists can be minted via "dzil new -P Author::KENTNL
   Some::Dist::Name". This profile is shipped in the ShareDir for this module name.
 - Consuming dists can now set 'git_versions = 1' as a flag to this plugin to use Git::NextVersion instead of
   AutoVersion::Relative.
 - Now ship .perltidyrc files with all dists by adding an exclusion to PruneCruft/GatherDir. Have to drop portability
   tests as a result.

 [Internals]
 - Internal Loading code replaced with Class::Load.

